        <updateDate>2022-06-14T12:01:15Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Muslim Brotherhood Terrorist Designation Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of State to submit to Congress a detailed report indicating whether the Muslim Brotherhood meets the criteria to be designated a foreign terrorist organization. If the report determines that the Muslim Brotherhood does not meet such criteria, it must provide a detailed justification as to which criteria have not been met.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
